<i>adjective</i>: 무시무시하다 [무시무시하다], 무섭다 [무섭따] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>무시무시하다 [무시무시하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. horrible; terrible; frightful</dd><br>
<dd>공포와 불안을 느끼게 할 정도로 무섭고 끔찍하다.</dd><br>
<dd>So fearful and dreadful as to make a person feel fear and anxiety.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tremendous; frightful</dd><br>
<dd>정도나 수준, 능력 등이 매우 심하거나 대단하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The degree or level of something, or the ability of a person, etc., being very high or remarkable.</dd><br>
<dt>무섭다 [무섭따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fearful; scared of</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상이 꺼려지거나 무슨 일이 일어날까 두렵다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling scared of something, or feeling afraid something might happen.</dd><br>
<dd>2. afraid; scared</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사람이나 상황이 대하기 어렵거나 피하고 싶다.</dd><br>
<dd>A person or situation being so dreadful as to make one want to avoid the person or thing.</dd><br>
<dd>3. frightful; tremendous</dd><br>
<dd>정도나 수준, 능력 등이 매우 심하거나 대단하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The degree or level of something, or the ability of a person, etc., being very high or remarkable.</dd><br>
<dd>4. as soon as</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이 일어나자마자 곧바로.</dd><br>
<dd>Immediately after something happens.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>